---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Our terms and conditions outline the rules, guidelines, and agreements for using our services."
  title="Terms & conditions Â· ODY Spatial"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-gray lg:prose-xl">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold">Terms and Conditions</h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-600 mt-4 text-sm"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2, 2025</p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to Ody Spatial. These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your use of our
          website and interior design services. By accessing our website or using our services, you
          agree to be bound by these Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. Services</h2>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.1 Interior Design Services</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>We provide interior design consultation, planning, and execution services</li>
          <li>All designs and proposals are subject to client approval</li>
          <li>Service scope and deliverables will be detailed in separate project agreements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.2 Online Booking</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            Appointments can be scheduled through our online booking system powered by Cal.com
          </li>
          <li>Consultation slots are subject to availability</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to reschedule appointments with reasonable notice</li>
        </ul>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.3 Payment Services</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Payment processing is handled through Polar.sh</li>
            <li>All prices are in United States Dollars (USD) unless otherwise stated</li>
            <li>Prices are subject to change with notice</li>
            <li>
              Exchange rates for international transactions are determined by your payment provider
            </li>
            <li>
              Additional foreign transaction fees may apply based on your payment method or bank
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.4 Currency and Pricing</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Our service rates are listed in United States Dollars (USD)</li>
            <li>International clients may see approximate conversions in their local currency</li>
            <li>The final charged amount will be in USD</li>
            <li>
              We are not responsible for any currency conversion fees imposed by your bank or
              payment provider
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. Booking and Payment Terms</h2>

          <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.1 Consultations</h3>
          <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Initial consultation fees must be paid at the time of booking</li>
            <li>Consultation duration and rates will be clearly displayed during booking</li>
            <li>48-hour cancellation notice required for full refund</li>
          </ul>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.2 Project Payments</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Project fees will be outlined in separate agreements in USD</li>
              <li>Payment schedules will be determined on a project basis</li>
              <li>Late payments may incur additional charges</li>
              <li>International wire transfers must cover all bank fees</li>
              <li>Minimum project value and consultation fees will be clearly stated in USD</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.3 Refund Policy</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Consultation cancellations with less than 48 hours notice are non-refundable</li>
              <li>
                Project deposits are non-refundable unless otherwise stated in project agreement
              </li>
              <li>Refund requests will be processed within 14 business days</li>
              <li>Refunds will be issued in USD to the original payment method</li>
              <li>
                Any currency conversion losses due to exchange rate fluctuations will not be covered
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. Booking and Payment Terms</h2>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.1 Consultations</h3>
            <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Initial consultation fees must be paid at the time of booking</li>
              <li>Consultation duration and rates will be clearly displayed during booking</li>
              <li>48-hour cancellation notice required for full refund</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.2 Project Payments</h3>
            <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Project fees will be outlined in separate agreements</li>
              <li>Payment schedules will be determined on a project basis</li>
              <li>Late payments may incur additional charges</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">3.3 Refund Policy</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Consultation cancellations with less than 48 hours notice are non-refundable</li>
              <li>
                Project deposits are non-refundable unless otherwise stated in project agreement
              </li>
              <li>Refund requests will be processed within 14 business days</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Intellectual Property</h2>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">4.1 Our Rights</h3>
            <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>All designs, drawings, and documents remain our intellectual property</li>
              <li>Portfolio rights are retained unless explicitly agreed otherwise</li>
              <li>Website content and images are protected by copyright</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">4.2 Client Materials</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Clients retain rights to their provided materials</li>
              <li>Permission required for portfolio use of completed projects</li>
              <li>Confidentiality of client information is maintained</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">5. Project Execution</h2>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">5.1 Timeline</h3>
            <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Project timelines are estimates and subject to change</li>
              <li>Delays due to external factors are not our responsibility</li>
              <li>Regular updates will be provided on project progress</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">5.2 Changes and Modifications</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Change requests must be submitted in writing</li>
              <li>Additional costs may apply to scope changes</li>
              <li>Timeline impacts will be communicated</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">6. Liability and Insurance</h2>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">6.1 Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>We maintain professional liability insurance</li>
              <li>Not liable for third-party contractor work</li>
              <li>Force majeure conditions apply</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">6.2 Client Responsibilities</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Accurate information provision</li>
              <li>Timely decision-making and responses</li>
              <li>Access to project sites as required</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">7. Termination</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Either party may terminate with written notice</li>
              <li>Outstanding payments remain due</li>
              <li>Completed work remains our intellectual property</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">8. Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
              <li>Disputes will be resolved through mediation first</li>
              <li>Singapore law governs these Terms</li>
              <li>Exclusive jurisdiction of Singapore courts</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p>
              We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective
              immediately upon posting on our website.
            </p>
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
    </div>

    <style>
      .prose {
        max-width: 65ch;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      }

      .prose h1 {
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }

      .prose h2 {
        color: #2a2a2a;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .prose h3 {
        color: #3a3a3a;
      }

      .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .prose ul {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .prose li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
    </style>
  </main>
</Layout>
